title: Texans quarterback Ryan Mallett says he got stuck in traffic, missing team flight
text:
Published By: Houston Chronicle Sports - Today 
"I got caught in traffic," Mallett said following a 44-26 loss to the Dolphins. "It's not the leadership role I need to exhibit."...
